); }; return ( GATE 2024 Marks Calculator (CSE S1/CSE S2/DA) Developed by Pritish Poswal window.open('https://twitter.com/pritishposwal')}> window.open('https://github.com/pritishposwal')}> window.open('https://linkedin.com/in/pritishposwal')}> Select Exam Type setExamType(e.target.value)} > } label="CSE S1" /> } label="CSE S2" /> } label="DA" /> setLink(e.target.value)} margin="normal" /> {results && ( Category Positive Marks Negative Marks Attempted Correct Incorrect Total Marks Aptitude {results.aptitudeScore.positive} {results.aptitudeScore.negative} {results.aptitudeScore.attempted} {results.aptitudeScore.correct} {results.aptitudeScore.incorrect} {results.aptitudeScore.total} Core {results.coreScore.positive} {results.coreScore.negative} {results.coreScore.attempted} {results.coreScore.correct} {results.coreScore.incorrect} {results.coreScore.total} Combined {results.combinedScore.positive} {results.combinedScore.negative} {results.combinedScore.attempted} {results.combinedScore.correct} {results.combinedScore.incorrect} {results.combinedScore.total}
)} {renderQuestionDetails()} © 2024 Developed by Pritish Poswal ); } export default App;
